2 HOUSE BILL 429
1 Annotated Code of Maryland
2 (2016 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
3 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
4 Article – Environment
5 Section 1–701(a)(1), (7), and (8)
