17 (2) “GRANT PROGRAM” MEANS THE WASTED FOOD REDUCTION AND
18 DIVERSION GRANT PROGRAM.
19 (3) “OVERBURDENED COMMUNITY” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN §
20 1–701 OF THIS ARTICLE.
21 (4) “UNDERSERVED COMMUNITY” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN §
22 1–701 OF THIS ARTICLE.
23 (5) “URBAN AGRICULTURAL PRODUCER” HAS THE MEANING STATED
24 IN § 2–2001 OF THE AGRICULTURE ARTICLE.
