6 COMMUNITY, AND ON–FARM COMPOSTING; OR
7 (5) TRANSITIONS FROM SINGLE–USE FOOD SERVICEWARE TO
8 DURABLE AND REUSABLE FOOD SERVICEWARE.
9 (G) IN AWARDING GRANTS UNDER THE GRANT PROGRAM, THE
10 DEPARTMENT, IN CONSULTATION WITH THE DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE,
11 SHALL PRIORITIZE PROJECTS:
12 (1) FOR WHICH THE APPLICANT CLEARLY DESCRIBES HOW THE
