18 LOCAL COMMUNITY;
19 (3) THAT PLAN TO PRODUCE COMPOST THAT MEETS THE
20 CLASSIFICATION OF “GENERAL USE” UNDER COMAR 15.18.04.05;
21 (4) THAT PLAN TO PRODUCE MINIMALLY CONTAMINATED COMPOST
22 THROUGH:
23 (I) PROCESSING ORGANIC MATERIALS THAT ARE SEPARATED
24 FROM PACKAGING PRIOR TO COLLECTION;
25 (II) NOT USING DEPACKAGERS; AND
26 (III) MEETING THE U.S. COMPOSTING COUNCIL’S SEAL OF
